VSujana Ranjani, featured young female vocalist Sandhyasri in a pleasing recital at Sabha's venue Hanuman Devasthanam, Sanathnagar, recently.Sandhya  is gifted with mellifluous voice with good vocal scope . She rendered thekirtanaswithsahityaclarity and made every composition enjoyable. In accompanying her on violin, Uma Sankar carefully elevated her recital adding his own imagination, especially inragaessays. K. Shyam Kumar accompanied on mridangam . Together, the young team of performers made the recital enjoyable.Sandhya  began withSaveri varnamin two speeds, displaying perfect timing andragamood. AfterSri MahaganapatiminAbhogiwith a briefswaraimprovisation, Sandhya took upKaanadafor a brief elaboration. Swati Tirunal'sMamava sada Jananiwas rendered well. Sandhya then came up  withPantuvarali. She shaped it up into a sweet melody and chose yet anotherkirtana, Sarasaksha Paripalayaof Swathi Tirunal. She took upnerevalatBhamini Samudayasaya, extending into beautifulswaras. Then cameEvarikai avatarainDevamanoharias preface for her majorragaeffortMohana.She presented popularkriti Mohana Rama.Good expression in thekirtanapart and technical beautification in thenerevalandswaraprastharaparts elevated the number to make it stand out  as the best piece.Taniby Shyamsundar was quite engaging. The end part had interestingThillanainBagesri.G.S.Bottom Template Starts
